data.description: Seller May Consider Closing Cost Contribution To Buyer! Excellent location near sporting facilities and the entertainment district. Come inside to see a spacious living room with wood flooring, neutral palette, high ceilings, and abundant natural light. The eat-in kitchen offers a pass-through window, built-in appliances, a pantry, a center island w/breakfast bar for quick meals, and a combination of recessed and pendant lighting. Upstairs, discover the ample primary bedroom featuring a full bathroom and a walk-in closet. Private backyard has a covered patio and grass area ideal for BBQ gatherings. Don't let this incredible property slip by!
